@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About StarEvents";
}

<section class="py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold mb-4">About StarEvents Ticketing System</h1>

        <p class="lead">
            StarEvents Pvt Ltd is a leading company in Sri Lanka that organizes large-scale 
            concerts, theatre shows, and cultural events. To support their growing audience 
            and digital-first strategy, StarEvents has introduced an Online Event Ticketing 
            Web Application.
        </p>

        <p>
            The system allows customers to browse upcoming events, book tickets online, 
            and make secure payments. Customers receive QR-coded e-tickets for seamless 
            entry validation at event venues.
        </p>

        <p>
            Event organizers can create, update, and manage events, set ticket prices, 
            and monitor ticket sales and revenue in real time. Administrators are given 
            tools to oversee system activity, manage users and venues, configure discounts 
            and loyalty programs, and generate overall sales and performance reports.
        </p>

        <p>
            With features like promotional discounts, loyalty points, booking history, 
            and digital ticket wallets, StarEvents Ticketing System provides a complete 
            solution for modern event management.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>
